<p begin="00:21.141" end="00:22.818" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L7"><span begin="00:21.141" end="00:21.290">The</span> <span begin="00:21.290" end="00:21.748">room</span> <span begin="00:21.748" end="00:22.014">where</span> <span begin="00:22.014" end="00:22.206">it</span> <span begin="00:22.206" end="00:22.818">happens</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">那个事发的房间</span></p><p begin="00:22.910" end="00:24.643" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L8"><span begin="00:22.910" end="00:23.078">The</span> <span begin="00:23.078" end="00:23.406">room</span> <span begin="00:23.406" end="00:23.740">where</span> <span begin="00:23.740" end="00:23.858">it</span> <span begin="00:23.858" end="00:24.643">happens</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">那个事发的房间</span></p><p begin="00:24.888" end="00:28.344" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L9"><span begin="00:24.888" end="00:25.209">You've</span> <span begin="00:25.209" end="00:25.652">kept</span> <span begin="00:25.652" end="00:25.934">me</span> <span begin="00:25.934" end="00:26.250">from</span> <span begin="00:26.250" end="00:26.437">the</span> <span begin="00:26.437" end="00:26.933">room</span> <span begin="00:26.933" end="00:27.212">where</span> <span begin="00:27.212" end="00:27.351">it</span> <span begin="00:27.351" end="00:28.344">happens</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">而你一直把我挡在那个事发的房间之外</span></p><p begin="00:28.512" end="00:31.729" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L10"><span begin="00:28.512" end="00:28.877">For</span> <span begin="00:28.877" end="00:29.135">the</span> <span begin="00:29.135" end="00:29.507">last</span> <span begin="00:29.507" end="00:31.729">time</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">这是最后一次了</span></p><p begin="00:38.238" end="00:40.689" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L11"><span begin="00:38.238" end="00:38.971">Dear</span> <span begin="00:38.971" end="00:39.801">Alexand</span><span begin="00:39.801" end="00:40.689">er</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">亲爱的亚历山大：</span></p><p begin="00:41.099" end="00:45.400" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L12"><span begin="00:41.099" end="00:41.356">I</span> <span begin="00:41.356" end="00:41.499">am</span> <span begin="00:41.499" end="00:41.963">slow</span> <span begin="00:41.963" end="00:42.229">to</span> <span begin="00:42.229" end="00:42.693">anger,</span> <span begin="00:43.248" end="00:43.433">but</span> <span begin="00:43.433" end="00:43.684">I</span> <span begin="00:44.123" end="00:44.510">toe</span> <span begin="00:44.510" end="00:44.682">the</span> <span begin="00:44.682" end="00:45.400">line</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我不轻易发怒，但我也有底线</span></p><p begin="00:45.490" end="00:47.422" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L13"><span begin="00:45.490" end="00:45.797">As</span> <span begin="00:45.797" end="00:45.921">I</span> <span begin="00:45.921" end="00:46.296">reckon</span> <span begin="00:46.296" end="00:46.540">with</span> <span begin="00:46.540" end="00:46.771">the</span> <span begin="00:46.771" end="00:47.422">effects</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">当我清算你的一生</span></p><p begin="00:47.422" end="00:49.353" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L14"><span begin="00:47.422" end="00:47.740">Of</span> <span begin="00:47.740" end="00:48.057">your</span> <span begin="00:48.057" end="00:48.493">life</span> <span begin="00:48.493" end="00:48.722">on</span> <span begin="00:48.722" end="00:49.353">mine</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">对我产生的影响时</span></p><p begin="00:49.679" end="00:51.912" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L15"><span begin="00:49.679" end="00:49.885">I</span> <span begin="00:49.885" end="00:50.235">look</span> <span begin="00:50.235" end="00:50.615">back</span> <span begin="00:50.615" end="00:50.807">on</span> <span begin="00:50.807" end="00:51.027">where</span> <span begin="00:51.027" end="00:51.223">I</span> <span begin="00:51.223" end="00:51.912">failed</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我回顾了那些我失败的地方</span></p><p begin="00:52.069" end="00:54.072" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L16"><span begin="00:52.069" end="00:52.336">And</span> <span begin="00:52.336" end="00:52.485">in</span> <span begin="00:52.485" end="00:52.937">every</span> <span begin="00:52.937" end="00:53.318">place</span> <span begin="00:53.318" end="00:53.599">I</span> <span begin="00:53.599" end="00:54.072">checked</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">在我检查过的每一个角落</span></p><p begin="00:54.383" end="00:58.156" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L17"><span begin="00:54.383" end="00:54.690">The</span> <span begin="00:54.690" end="00:55.086">only</span> <span begin="00:55.086" end="00:55.587">common</span> <span begin="00:55.587" end="00:55.977">thread</span> <span begin="00:55.977" end="00:56.221">has</span> <span begin="00:56.221" end="00:56.496">been</span> <span begin="00:56.496" end="00:56.770">your</span> <span begin="00:56.770" end="00:58.156">disrespect</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">唯一的共同点就是你对我的轻视</span></p><p begin="00:58.501" end="01:00.567" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L18"><span begin="00:58.501" end="00:58.783">Now</span> <span begin="00:58.783" end="00:58.991">you</span> <span begin="00:58.991" end="00:59.342">call</span> <span begin="00:59.342" end="00:59.632">me</span> <span begin="00:59.632" end="01:00.567">amoral</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">现在你称我为毫无道德的人</span></p><p begin="01:00.871" end="01:02.744" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L19"><span begin="01:00.871" end="01:01.103">A</span> <span begin="01:01.103" end="01:01.803">dangerous</span> <span begin="01:01.803" end="01:02.744">disgrace</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">一个危险的耻辱</span></p><p begin="01:02.854" end="01:04.696" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L20"><span begin="01:02.854" end="01:03.071">If</span> <span begin="01:03.071" end="01:03.304">you've</span> <span begin="01:03.304" end="01:03.613">got</span> <span begin="01:03.613" end="01:04.143">something</span> <span begin="01:04.143" end="01:04.362">to</span> <span begin="01:04.362" end="01:04.696">say</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">如果你有什么话要说</span></p><p begin="01:04.706" end="01:07.490" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L21"><span begin="01:04.706" end="01:05.149">Name</span> <span begin="01:05.149" end="01:05.278">a</span> <span begin="01:05.278" end="01:05.870">time</span> <span begin="01:05.870" end="01:06.118">and</span> <span begin="01:06.118" end="01:06.454">place,</span> <span begin="01:06.531" end="01:06.861">face</span> <span begin="01:06.861" end="01:07.076">to</span> <span begin="01:07.076" end="01:07.490">face</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">选个时间地点，我们面对面解决</span></p><p begin="01:07.571" end="01:12.916" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L22"><span begin="01:07.571" end="01:07.979">I</span> <span begin="01:07.979" end="01:08.296">have</span> <span begin="01:08.296" end="01:08.664">the</span> <span begin="01:08.664" end="01:09.363">honor</span> <span begin="01:09.363" end="01:09.715">to</span> <span begin="01:09.715" end="01:10.099">be</span> <span begin="01:10.559" end="01:10.698">your</span> <span begin="01:10.698" end="01:11.742">obedient</span> <span begin="01:11.806" end="01:12.916">servant</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我有幸成为您忠实的仆人</span></p><p begin="01:13.350" end="01:14.575" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L23"><span begin="01:13.350" end="01:13.744">A</span> <span begin="01:13.744" end="01:14.094">dot</span> <span begin="01:14.094" end="01:14.575">Burr</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">A·伯尔</span></p><p begin="01:14.820" end="01:16.123" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L24"><span begin="01:14.820" end="01:15.173">Mr.</span> <span begin="01:15.173" end="01:15.547">Vice</span> <span begin="01:15.547" end="01:16.123">President</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">副总统先生：</span></p><p begin="01:16.133" end="01:18.321" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L25"><span begin="01:16.133" end="01:16.445">I</span> <span begin="01:16.445" end="01:16.650">am</span> <span begin="01:16.650" end="01:16.859">not</span> <span begin="01:16.859" end="01:17.007">the</span> <span begin="01:17.007" end="01:17.361">reason</span> <span begin="01:17.361" end="01:17.539">no</span> <span begin="01:17.539" end="01:17.719">one</span> <span begin="01:17.719" end="01:18.121">trusts</span> <span begin="01:18.121" end="01:18.321">you</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">没人信任你，原因并不在我</span></p><p begin="01:18.379" end="01:19.770" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L26"><span begin="01:18.379" end="01:18.600">No</span> <span begin="01:18.600" end="01:18.725">one</span> <span begin="01:18.725" end="01:19.005">knows</span> <span begin="01:19.005" end="01:19.215">what</span> <span begin="01:19.215" end="01:19.354">you</span> <span begin="01:19.354" end="01:19.770">believe</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">没人知道你到底信仰什么</span></p><p begin="01:19.922" end="01:22.256" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L27"><span begin="01:19.922" end="01:20.107">I</span> <span begin="01:20.107" end="01:20.265">will</span> <span begin="01:20.265" end="01:20.490">not</span> <span begin="01:20.490" end="01:21.162">equivocate</span> <span begin="01:21.162" end="01:21.317">on</span> <span begin="01:21.317" end="01:21.494">my</span> <span begin="01:21.494" end="01:22.256">opinion</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我绝不会对自己的观点含糊其辞</span></p><p begin="01:22.364" end="01:24.201" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L28"><span begin="01:22.364" end="01:22.615">I</span> <span begin="01:22.615" end="01:22.839">have</span> <span begin="01:22.839" end="01:23.136">always</span> <span begin="01:23.136" end="01:23.417">worn</span> <span begin="01:23.417" end="01:23.537">it</span> <span begin="01:23.537" end="01:23.660">on</span> <span begin="01:23.660" end="01:23.760">my</span> <span begin="01:23.760" end="01:24.201">sleeve</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我总是把立场表露无遗<